      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's just so exhausting. everyone keeps telling me \"it'll get better\" or to \"stay strong\" but they don't get it. they aren't the ones living in this body. sometimes it feels like the only way to actually get some peace is to just... not be here anymore. like, isn't there a kind of mercy in just stopping the cycle?",
